// L E S S O N  P.D.F
▶️  https://bit.ly/FrenchWinterVerbs

In this lesson you'll learn some useful French verbs to talk about winter, and you'll also learn how to conjugate first group verbs in the present tense. We'll also touch on French pronunciation and you'll get to hear me talk to you in French, recounting a few winter experiences. So, in effect this lesson contains a bit of everything, from listening comprehension to vocabulary, grammar and a bit of pronunciation thrown in for good measure. I hope you enjoy it.
